      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/trivia/work/23859166-one-summer-america-1927">Trivia About One Summer: Ameri...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
        <div class="mediumText">
          29 trivia questions
          <br />
          
        </div>
        <a class="actionLink" style="float: right;" href="/trivia/work/23859166-one-summer-america-1927">More quizzes &amp; trivia...</a>
